luehour" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4078000&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1560120607" alt="TheBlueHour" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4078000)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thebluehour" >TheBlueHour</a></span> for clearing the cobwebs and helps with big cuts.</li> <li>Finally to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1560120607" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" >Weryllium</a></span> for help with polish.</li> </ul> <p>Images here:</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Mailbox</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Mailbox</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Creative Commons<br /> <a href="https://ccsearch.creativecommons.org/photos/f9d2169c-e03b-40fe-a33f-075711d20d80">https://ccsearch.creativecommons.org/photos/f9d2169c-e03b-40fe-a33f-075711d20d80</a></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Package</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Package</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Creative commons &quot;paper bag&quot; and then the writing is my handwriting.<br /> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Brown_Paper_Bag_Texture_Free_Creative_COmmons_(6816220224).jpg">h